WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.500
[Generation Nano game: Nanotubes Lab screen. A conductivity tester board displays a hexagonal grid of nanotube chirality values.]

00:00:02.500 --> 00:00:05.500
[Nanotubes labeled with chirality coordinates (n,m) travel along a conveyor belt. Two sorting bins are labeled "SEMI" and "METAL".]

00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:09.042
[A nanotube is sorted into the semiconducting bin. Mission progress and score update on the left panel. Researcher video panel visible in the corner.]
